rComments: I have no idea what others are talking about when they complain about her teaching methods. By far one of best professor i've ever had. Also the presentations consist of the actual 15 minute presentation followed by a half hour discussing where she expands on the concepts in amazing detail.

She doesn't teach!! The entire course was other students giving presentations!! NOT what I signed up for... I didn't pay almost $1000 for that. Class puts me to sleep and class participation is sooo low, which is really bad because it's a seminar so it should be fairly high. Most of the students don't come to the class.
Prof. Pugliese makes tackling very difficult texts enjoyable; she's so learned and yet so entirely accessible.  Studying any subject with her would be completely worthwhile.
She was so helpful and cared about her students.  She even suggested books to refer to for other classes, that's how nice she was!
